ner-container\">\n<p>Three days is the perfect amount of time to see everything. However, beautiful sunshine, relaxation, and a traditional French atmosphere could keep you here for longer!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40.jpg\" alt=\"ile de re france \"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ile de re france \" class=\"wp-image-60913 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02145319\/Ile-de-Re-france40-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\