ntent\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02143444\/Ile-de-Re-france38-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-ars-en-re\">Ars-en-Re<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit the charming village of Ars-en-Re, one of the island&#x2019;s 10 villages, known for its iconic church spire that can be seen across the island. Ars-en-Re is one of the most beautiful villages in France and it&#x2019;s no surprise why, with its cobbled streets, colorful shutters, and climbing flowers. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1.jpg\" alt=\"ile de re france best things to do village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ile de re france best things to do village\" class=\"wp-image-60790 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-Re-france1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095542\/Ile-de-R