ad now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02173237\/ile-de-re-france-2-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02173237\/ile-de-re-france-2-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Best Things To Do in Ile de R&#xE9;, Atlantic Coast, France\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-saint-martin-de-re\"><strong>Saint-Martin-de-Re<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>At the opposite end of the island, discover the ancient village of Saint-Martin-de-Re. The most impressive characteristic of this beautiful place is the fact that it sits within a star-shaped fort. Its history and preservation are so unique that it was awarded UNESCO heritage status in 2008. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095614\/Ile-de-Re-france4.jpg\" alt=\"ile de re france best things to do beautiful villages\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ile de re france best things to do beautiful villages\" class=\"wp-image-60796 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095614\/Ile-de-Re-france4.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-con