p-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Seeing the fort is one of the top things to do on Ile de Re, however, the village itself is great too! Stroll through the old streets with its narrow alleys, charming cottages, and traditional wells, stopping off at one of the many fantastic cafes and bistros. Don&#x2019;t forget to climb to the top of the bell tower for panoramic views out across the village and surrounding nature.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The must-see UNESCO world heritage sites!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02135136\/Ile-de-Re-france31-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"france village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"france village\" class=\"wp-image-60888 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02135136\/Ile-de-Re-france31-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02135136\/Ile-de-Re-france31-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02135136\/Ile-de-Re-france31-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\