and even discover tasting techniques and get one of their very nicely designed bottles. It&#x2019;s worth visiting just for the stunning location of the estate, right at the ocean&#x2019;s edge. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2.jpg\" alt=\"ile de re best things to do vineyards\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ile de re best things to do vineyards\" class=\"wp-image-60792 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-france2-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/30095554\/Ile-de-Re-fr