8\" alt=\"salt marshes france\" class=\"wp-image-60871 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02121339\/Ile-de-Re-france25-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-6-visit-an-oyster-farm\">6. <strong>Visit an Oyster Farm&#xA0;<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>France is famous worldwide for oysters: a luxury aphrodisiac which people either love or hate! Whether you want to eat them or not, learning about how they are harvested is a top thing to do on Ile de Re. To do so, visit an Oyster farm, like the one belonging to the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.huitresetmare.fr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Bouyer family<\/a>, where you will learn about the three-year journey from breeding to plate! <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also visit:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/aix-island-rochefort\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Aix Island and Rochefort<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/02135126\/Ile-de-Re-france30.jpg\" alt=\"ile de re france oyster farm\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ile de re france oyster farm\" class=\"wp-image-60886 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"htt