                 <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> you are given an audio guide as part of the entry price. However, you can also rent binoculars, and telescopes before starting out on the nature reserve loop. You can see prices to rent equipment <a href=\"https:\/\/www.maisondufier.fr\/en\/opening-hours-and-prices\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here. <\/a>If you want to learn even more, you can book one of the organized nature walks with a guide.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"ile de re best things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"ile de re best things to do\" class=\"wp-image-60844 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01202649\/Ile-de-Re-france15-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploa